org.apache.calcite.adapter.java

接口 JavaTypeFactory

  • 所有超级接口:
    RelDataTypeFactory
    所有已知实现类:
    JavaTypeFactoryExtImpl, JavaTypeFactoryImpl

    public interface JavaTypeFactory
extends RelDataTypeFactory
    Type factory that can register Java classes as record types.

    • 嵌套类概要

      • 从接口继承的嵌套类/接口 org.apache.calcite.rel.type.RelDataTypeFactory

        RelDataTypeFactory.Builder, RelDataTypeFactory.FieldInfo, RelDataTypeFactory.FieldInfoBuilder

      Creates a record type based upon the public fields of a Java class.

      RelDataType createType(Type type)
      Creates a type, deducing whether a record, scalar or primitive type is needed.
